@postUrl = http://localhost:3002
@identityUrl = http://localhost:3001
@moderationUrl = http://localhost:3003

### ───────────────────────────────
### HEALTH CHECKS
### all three services must be running
### ───────────────────────────────

### 1. Identity health
GET {{identityUrl}}/health

###

### 2. Post health
GET {{postUrl}}/health

###

### 3. Moderation health
GET {{moderationUrl}}/health


### ───────────────────────────────
### SETUP — get token from identity
### ───────────────────────────────

### 4. Login
POST {{identityUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

