### ───────────────────────────────
### FULL PIPELINE TEST
### ───────────────────────────────

### 5. Create post — watch moderation console after this
POST {{postUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "community",
  "title": "Stray dog near park gate",
  "body": "There is a friendly stray near the main gate, someone please adopt"
}

###

### 6. Get post immediately — should return 404 (still pending)
GET {{postUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}

###

### 7. Wait 2-3 seconds for moderation, then get again
### if moderation approved it → post now visible
GET {{postUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}


### ───────────────────────────────
### TEST FLAGGING BEHAVIOR
### ───────────────────────────────

### 8. Create post with spam text — should get flagged by worker
POST {{postUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "classified",
  "title": "Click here to earn free money guaranteed income",
  "body": "Whatsapp me for deal, work from home earn 50000 daily"
}

###

### 9. Check moderation queue — flagged post should appear here
GET {{moderationUrl}}/moderation/queue


### ───────────────────────────────
### HUMAN REVIEW
### ───────────────────────────────

### 10. Human approves a flagged post
POST {{moderationUrl}}/moderation/{{postId}}/decision
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision": "approved",
  "reason": "False positive — legitimate listing"
}

###

### 11. Human removes a post
POST {{moderationUrl}}/moderation/{{postId}}/decision
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "decision": "removed",
  "reason": "Confirmed spam"
}